==============================================================================
============================= PANDOC LUA-FILTERS =============================
==============================================================================

All themes also contains a copy of the “task-list.lua” pandoc filter taken
from “lua-filters” project:

-   https://github.com/pandoc/lua-filters

“lua-filters” is Copyright (c) 2017-2018 pandoc, released under MIT License.

This pandoc filter adds support of GFM style Task-Lists in markdown documents.
The source code of the filter was modified to disable CSS injection and
prevent conflicts with “header-includes” in YAML headers. More details on the
changes can be found in the source file’s comments.

